        " الْحُبْلَى تُطَلَّقُ تَطْلِيقَةً وَاحِدَةً ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "And from him, from Abdullah Bin Jabala, and Safwan Bin Yahya, from Ibn Bukeyr, from Abu Baseer, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The pregnant woman is divorced with one divorce’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "4. It is narrated from the narrator of the previous Hadith from ‘Abd Allah ibn Jabalah and from Safwan ibn Yahya from ibn Bukayr from abu Basir who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘A pregnant woman is divorced once.’” "
        ]
      }
